                <h1>How to Change Your iPhone Lock Screen Wallpaper</h1>
                <p>Changing the lock screen wallpaper on your iPhone is a quick and easy process. Simply open the Settings app, tap on "Wallpaper," and select "Choose a New Wallpaper." You can choose from dynamic, stills, or your own photos. Adjust the image to fit perfectly, then tap "Set" to apply it to your lock screen, home screen, or both.</p>
